resources UK(12)
notes
We would like to run PAMS when a high-speed stream interacts with the
magnetosphere as this optimises chances of a ULF wave generated by the
Kelvin-Helmholtz instability. For this reason, we are overbooking the PAMS run
with the intention of cancelling a few runs closer to the time.
